summary: This is an email exchange regarding a federal trial subpoena. A Special Agent from the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk sends a trial subpoena to an individual, who responds about requesting time off from work to comply.

keyFacts: An FBI Special Agent from the Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk in New York sent a federal trial subpoena on November 15, 2021.
The recipient of the subpoena is coordinating time off from work to comply with it, as indicated in a response on November 16, 2021.
The document is related to ongoing federal legal proceedings, likely connected to child exploitation or human trafficking cases.
